PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FSeven men from a criminal network who
OL,7,Fstole more than #100,000 worth of
OL,8,Fwatches, artwork and designer goods in
OL,9,Fsmash-and-grab robberies have been
OL,10,Fjailed for a total of 22 years.
OL,12,FRobbers used sledgehammers, bricks and
OL,13,Fa Ford Fiesta to crash their way into
OL,14,Fa series of high-end London stores
OL,15,Fbetween May and August 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FBy looking at vehicle movements and
OL,7,Fthousands of hours of CCTV footage,
OL,8,Fpolice confirmed the string of
OL,9,Foffences were all linked to the same
OL,10,F"criminal network" operating near
OL,11,FPaddington in west London.
OL,13,FChristopher Gibbs, 43; George O'Hare,
OL,14,F42; Paul Hughes, 42; Anthony Munday,
OL,15,F40; Lee James McCready, 46; Matthew
OL,16,FWindrass, 50; and David Rigelsford,
OL,17,F37, were sentenced at Kingston Crown
OL,18,FCourt.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FOne of the defendants, McCready, of
OL,7,FUxbridge, took part in a robbery where
OL,8,Falmost #60,000 worth of watches and
OL,9,Fjewellery were stolen from Suttons and
OL,10,FRobertsons store on Edgware Road.
OL,12,FCCTV footage seen in court showed two
OL,13,Fmen rushing up to the shop front
OL,14,Fwearing balaclavas and carrying
OL,15,Fsledgehammers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FThe two men, identified as McCready
OL,7,Fand Windrass, proceeded to snatch
OL,8,Fwatches and jewellery through the
OL,9,Fwindows before running back to a
OL,10,F"getaway driver" in a silver Jaguar,
OL,11,Fidentified as Munday.
OL,13,FWilliam Sneddon, prosecuting, said:
OL,14,F"On seeing the two males leave via the
OL,15,Fstore's security cameras, Mr Keaney
OL,16,F(the store manager) exited the store.
OL,17,FA large crowd had gathered and a lot
OL,18,Fof people were filming.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@PO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,F"He assessed that around five watches
OL,7,Fand some jewellery items, valued at a
OL,8,Fminimum of #59,930.00, had been
OL,9,Fstolen. The whole incident lasted
OL,10,Fapproximately nine minutes."
OL,12,FDefending Munday, Kane Sharpe said:
OL,13,F"The sledgehammers were not carried as
OL,14,Fweapons but as tools, to carry out
OL,15,Fwhat was essentially a smash-and-grab
OL,16,Fburglary."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@\O]uD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FIn another burglary caught on CCTV,
OL,7,Finvolving Gibbs, O'Hare and Hughes,
OL,8,Fthe robbers used a Ford Fiesta to
OL,9,Fcrash through the doors of a Fendi
OL,10,Fstore on Sloane Street.
OL,12,FThey can then be seen grabbing
OL,13,Fdesigner handbags before escaping
OL,14,Fusing a motorbike and a silver
OL,15,FMercedes.
OL,17,FMr Sneddon said: "Whilst the Fiesta
OL,18,Fwas ramming the store's doors, the
OL,19,Fpassenger from the Mercedes and the
OL,20,Fmotorcyclist stood on the pavement
OL,21,Fnearby.
OL,26,@yD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,F"After the third ram of the doors, the
OL,7,Fdriver of the Fiesta got out of the
OL,8,Fvehicle and joined the other two men
OL,9,Fwho had entered the Fendi store. The
OL,10,Fdriver of the Mercedes remained in the
OL,11,Fvehicle during the offence."
OL,13,FGibbs was also sentenced for using a
OL,14,F"paving block" to smash through the
OL,15,Flocked front door of Clarendon Fine
OL,16,FArt before stealing two pieces of
OL,17,Fframed art, collectively valued at
OL,18,F#66,500, along with another unknown
OL,19,Fman.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]vD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FAcross the group, five successful
OL,7,Fburglaries of London shops were
OL,8,Fcommitted between May and July 2025,
OL,9,Fwith a similar technique being used
OL,10,Feach time. A total of #146,356 worth
OL,11,Fof items were stolen during those
OL,12,Fincidents.
OL,14,FThere were also two unsuccessful
OL,15,Fburglaries of an apothecary in
OL,16,FMarylebone and a watch shop in
OL,17,FWestminster, the court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FRigelsford, of Kilburn, was also
OL,7,Fseparately convicted of a hotel
OL,8,Frobbery, two car thefts and an
OL,9,Fattempted theft of a rucksack from a
OL,10,Fvehicle.
OL,12,FThe prosecution said a blue Mini
OL,13,FCooper stolen by Rigelsford on May 22
OL,14,Flast year was used as a "getaway"
OL,15,Fvehicle in a burglary of Phillips
OL,16,FAuction House where items to a value
OL,17,Fof #610,500 would be stolen four days
OL,18,Flater.
OL,26,@vD@YOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FNo-one has yet been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with that incident, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard.
OL,10,FGibbs, McCready, Windrass, O'Hare and
OL,11,FMunday were located and arrested in a
OL,12,Fseries of co-ordinated raids on August
OL,13,F5 2025.
OL,15,FHughes and Rigelsford were arrested
OL,16,Fand charged for their involvement on
OL,17,FSeptember 29 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Scott
OL,7,FMather, from the Met's Flying Squad,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We realise these attacks on
OL,9,Fluxury stores have had a significant
OL,10,Fimpact on business owners and the
OL,11,Fcommunities around them.
OL,13,F"Our detectives worked quickly,
OL,14,Festablishing common patterns between
OL,15,Fthe attacks to link them to one
OL,16,Fcriminal network. Forensic analysis
OL,17,Fand fast-paced CCTV inquiries were
OL,18,Fthen able to identify the suspects.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1773918340
OL,3,CGang sentenced to 22 years for series
OL,4,Cof smash-and-grab robberies in London
OL,6,F"This is a clear message to anyone who
OL,7,Fthinks they can carry out smash-and-
OL,8,Fgrab raids in London ` we will
OL,9,Fidentify you, we will track you down
OL,10,Fand we will bring you to justice."
